My bug is based on TIMOB-384 - it was created and closed in 1 minute with absolutely meaningless comment
{quote}Duplicate of a billion tableview rendering speed bugs.{quote} 

I was not able to find any of those billion speed bugs using text search and labels from the bug, there's also no links to corresponding task or future releases. Can anyone please tell me, when and what will be done with tableview rendering speed? It's major part of almost any kind of iOS application.
